name: MATH 194
title: Senior Seminar
description: Designed to expose the student to topics not normally covered in the standard courses. The format varies from year to year. In recent years each student has written a paper and presented a lecture on it to the class.

pre_req_data.text: Prerequisite(s): satisfaction of the Entry Level Writing and Composition requirements;  MATH 103A or MATH 105A or MATH 110 or MATH 111A or MATH 111T or MATH 117. Enrollment priority is given to seniors; juniors may request permission from the undergraduate vice chair.
